Description:
    Generates configuration for the Stripe gem

Example:
    bin/rails generate stripe_initializer

    This will create:
        config/initializers/stripe.rb
        db/migrate/XXXXXXXXXXXXXX_add_stripe_id_to_users.rb
        db/migrate/XXXXXXXXXXXXXX_add_premium_until_to_users.rb (subscription)
        db/migrate/XXXXXXXXXXXXXX_add_premium_to_users.rb (payment)
        app/controllers/stripe/checkout_sessions_controller.rb
        app/controller/stripe/webhooks_controller.rb
    
    This will update:
        app/models/user.rb
        config/routes.rb
